%% Diagram: Magic Pocket read path
%% Type: sequence
%%{init: {'htmlLabels': false}}%%
sequenceDiagram
    participant C as Client
    participant FE as Frontend
    participant BI as Block Index
    participant RT as Repl Table
    participant O as OSDs

    C->>FE: GET(hash)
    FE->>BI: lookup hash
    BI-->>FE: cell, bucket, checksum
    FE->>RT: lookup volume
    RT-->>FE: volume + OSDs
    alt replicated volume
        FE->>O: read from one OSD
        O-->>FE: block
    else erasure-coded volume
        FE->>O: read shard from primary OSD
        O-->>FE: block (or trigger reconstruction)
    end
    FE-->>C: block bytes
